Title: To the Valley!
Description:
This sealed communication was sent for you, along with urgent orders to travel to the Valley of Emperors in Kun-Lai Summit.

This looks serious. I'd not delay if I were you.

Speak to Tak-Tak for transportation.
ObjectivesText: Find your "Friend from Silvermoon" at the Valley of Emperors. Speak to Tak-Tak at Domination Point for transportation.
